{"tid":2411300,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Angelababy遭大陸作家鬧爆逼改名 陶傑出手幫改名：安琪拉嬰兒","createTime":"2021-02-17T08:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T09:40:06.000Z","uid":130626,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"aeceaf5975e3a4b19808299073ebd015b6b6e10a","tid":2411300,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:38:33.000Z","msg":"喺大陸有「悲情詩人」之稱兼自稱係「第7代導演」嘅劉信達，經常在微博開火炮轟藝人，狙擊過謝霆鋒、陳小春、王寶強及楊冪等，而劉信達最新嘅目標，就係近年喺大陸發展順風順水嘅Angelababy（楊穎），鬧爆Baby作為一個中國人，但一直用英文名喺大陸搵食，如此「玻璃心」，搞到才子陶傑忍唔住出手，要幫Baby改中文藝名。<br />\n<br />\n曾叫Angelababy引退<br />\n一向鍾意四處焫火頭嘅劉信達，早幾日喺微博出post，指Baby明明身為中國人，偏偏用英文名，令人以為她是外國人，又指大陸人對外國的節日及洋化覺得反感，所以希望Baby對自己個英文名反感，用返中文名喺大陸發展。<br />\n<br />\n他更貼心提醒Baby：「西方人對應的是東方人，而不是南方人，不要無知者無畏，不要無聊當有趣！」其實劉信達並唔係第一次狙擊Baby，早喺2019年當時有報道稱Baby有女fans喺機場畀保安打，加上同黃曉明傳婚變等，劉信達曾出post指若果傳聞屬實，Baby應該自己選擇引退。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210217/SOBCZKFVBVEEZB3CXQBMO23ISY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210217%2FSOBCZKFVBVEEZB3CXQBMO23ISY%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN20bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=1fc7867d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210217%2FSOBCZKFVBVEEZB3CXQBMO23ISY%2F&h=e531e66f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210217/SOBCZKFVBVEEZB3CXQBMO23ISY/</a>"},{"pid":"d9309a869e6f42ac32db606e89424c152199ed48","tid":2411300,"uid":8902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:41:40.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我</span></span>"},{"pid":"4b3c4f8551b6543b1a9b6c8d1733784fffd8e491","tid":2411300,"uid":256943,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:43:12.000Z","msg":"安琪拉悲b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2cef8fc0487d21fa766003eea01ca38674508a0","tid":2411300,"uid":139173,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021